## Project Workflow

1. Cleaned dataset (removed NULLS, formatted date column)
2. Imported data into Power BI
3. Created relationships between tables
4. Created DAX measures & calculated columns
5. Designed dashboard with:
   - KPIs (Total Sales, Profit, Orders)
   - Bar chart (Top Products)
   - Pie chart (Category-wise Sales)
   - Line chart (Monthly Sales Trend)
   - Map (Sales by Location)
   - Slicers (Category, City, Year)

## Tools Used
- Power BI
- Excel
- DAX
